title: Spy
subTitle: An agent investigates the death of his elder brother with the help of his fellow agents. However, his actions lead to the discovery of a nuclear plot against India.

title: Vardi Ki Aan
subTitle: An upright police officer vows to punish the culprits involved in the brutal rape of a young woman. However, his investigations unravel a shocking secret about his own father's despicable crimes.

title: Dackalti
subTitle: An ingenious conman embarks on a mission to find a girl and transport her back to Mumbai. However, the fraudster's life takes an unexpected turn after he falls in love with his target.

title: RX 100
subTitle: Shiva has a passionate affair with Indu, a politician's daughter from the city. However, when they get separated, he becomes angry and prone to extreme violence.

title: Kumari Jille Ke Thugs
subTitle: Caught in the turmoil of prison life, a determined man forges alliances with fellow inmates, plotting a daring plan to escape and regain their freedom.

title: Geetanjali 2
subTitle: Sreenu receives a directorial offer from Vishnu to shoot in a bungalow. Later, him and his crew realise that Vishnu orchestrated the ploy to seek revenge by trapping them in a haunted house.

title: Veeram
subTitle: Two brothers, raised by their sister, take opposite path, one honest, the other criminal. When tragedy strikes and the criminal brother dies, the honest one seeks vengeance.

title: Satyabhama
subTitle: ACP Satyabhama embarks on an investigation into a missing person case, which leads her to uncover dark secrets hidden within the town. However, as she delves deeper, her past begins to haunt her.

title: Saindhav
subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: Chor Bazaar
subTitle: Bachchan Saab, a small-time thief, is in love with a girl from Chor Bazaar, which is famous for stolen goods. However, his life turns upside down when he stumbles across a stolen diamond.

title: Duniya
subTitle: An honest worker, Mohan, endures many years in prison after being framed for his employer's murder. Later, upon his release, he embarks on a relentless quest for revenge.

title: Express Khiladi
subTitle: A pantry worker and a make-up artist develop a romance aboard a runaway train, where they must confront dangerous challenges to save themselves and others.

title: Indian Soldier Never On Holiday
subTitle: An army officer sets out to save the people of his country when he learns that an entire network of terrorists are operating in the city and are planning to carry out multiple terror attacks.

title: Aakhri Yudh
subTitle: Babji, a loan recovery agent, decides to help Kavya when he finds her being chased by her family. However, Kavya's brother thinks that Babji and her sister are lovers and attacks his family.

title: Pichaikkaran 2
subTitle: Sathya is a poor man in search of his sister, who has been kidnapped by human traffickers. However, an illegal brain transplant puts him in the shoes of a billionaire named Vijay.

title: MCA: Middle Class Abbayi
subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Surya's Saturday
subTitle: A vigilante fights against injustice using his own unqiue moral code, where he only comes out to play on Saturdays.

title: Gaalodu
subTitle: After fighting with a villager's son, Raju leaves for the big city, and there he meets Shukla, a nice woman from a rich family. However, this chance meeting could change Raju's life.

title: Gaalodu

title: Maharathi
subTitle: After his boss, Jai Singh, commits suicide, Subhash, a chauffeur, conspires to get his insurance money. He then teams up with Jai's wife, Mallika, to make the suicide look like a well-planned murder.

title: Arjuna Phalguna
subTitle: A village man and his friends find out that the local bank wants to seize the house of one of them. So, they resort to various means to stop their friend from being homeless.

title: Dear Ghilli
subTitle: Ghilli, a dog, navigates through several challenges and experiences with his owner as both of them attempt to win the hearts of their lovers.

title: LIE
subTitle: Sathyam and Chaitra meet unexpectedly in their pursuit of making quick money. Soon, after they fall in love, Sathyam encounters Padmanabham, a criminal on the run from the Indian police.

title: Pogaru
subTitle: A local thug stands up against the atrocities committed on common people and fights to secure justice for them, thus earning the public's respect and affection.

title: The Masterpiece
subTitle: A young man falls in with the wrong crowd and strays from heroic deeds. However, an accidental encounter with danger forces him to change his ways.

title: Custody
subTitle: A police constable's life takes a drastic turn when he is entrusted with producing a criminal in court. While the mobster remains under his custody, Shiva must dodge every threat to keep him alive.

title: Madhagaja
subTitle: The wife of one of two rival dons sends her son to a distant land to shield him from their relentless feud. However, the son, raised as an orphan, eventually returns to the brutal world of violence.

title: ACP Shiva
subTitle: An IPS officer treads the path of corruption, but when his dishonest ways prove costly, he must decide whether to seek righteous revenge.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.
